npc/gatekeeper: Far enough. This is the last gate before the core, and it does not open for free.
npc/gatekeeper: The key is out here in the bait yard — buried among the coins that lie. Every gold platform that glitters is begging you to trust it, and most will drop you the instant you do.
npc/gatekeeper: Find the real key, ignore the fake shine, and bring it back to me. Then, and only then, does the way ahead open.
